import React, { Component } from "react";
import Navbar from "./components/Navbar";
import News from "./components/news";
import "./App.css";
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from "react-router-dom";
import Scrool from "./components/ScrollToTop";

export class App extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Router>
          <Navbar />
          <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/general">
              <News
                key="general"
                pageSize={12}
                category="general"
                country="in"
              />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/business">
              <News
                key="business"
                pageSize={12}
                category="business"
                country="in"
              />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/entertainment">
              <News
                key="entertainment"
                pageSize={12}
                category="entertainment"
                country="in"
              />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/health">
              <News key="health" pageSize={12} category="health" country="in" />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/science">
              <News
                key="science"
                pageSize={12}
                category="science"
                country="in"
              />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/technology">
              <News
                key="technology"
                pageSize={12}
                category="technology"
                country="in"
              />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/sports">
              <News key="sports" pageSize={12} category="sports" country="in" />
            </Route>
          </Switch>
          <ScrollToTop />
        </Router>

      </>
    );
  }
}

export default App;
